    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/469a0e551c8e3b0d1ea42b928c068c78.poster.avif?t=1695654699\" width=616 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/469a0e551c8e3b0d1ea42b928c068c78.webm?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/469a0e551c8e3b0d1ea42b928c068c78.mp4?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在可预见的未来，人类已经将目光投向了太空。太空探索的新时代到来了。在移民太阳系后，开启了探索与殖民新世界和新恒星系的时代。以前被认为不可想象事情，如今已经成为现实。科学已经达到了前所未有的高度，世界各地的人们团结起来，忘记了自古以来的冲突和内部斗争。<br>然而，伴随着人类生活中的一个个重大发现，同时也面临着新的问题。期待已久的，与地外文明的接触，使人类陷入了新一轮的军事冲突，争夺资源和适宜居住的土地，激化了不同物种之间的矛盾。<br>银河地图不断涌现出新玩家，大量的血腥战争不断发生。一个来自银河系中心的新对手正在靠近我们，他的力量无从估量，他的意图无人知晓。<br>玩家将以星际舰队船长詹姆斯•达克（James Dacker）的身份操纵飞船。与一支新的队伍在破旧的飞船上并肩作战，你将看到银河系最偏远的角落，与众多敌人展开战斗，与整个舰队展开激烈战斗，不仅要保护地球，还要保护全人类。<br><br><strong>各种玩法。</strong><br>在外太空、行星表面、密集的小行星带作战，还可以在巨大的空间站内作战。驾驶星际舰队的重型巡洋舰和小型歼击强击机。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/3ea51c43b5bbb93391aa95cd519d787b.poster.avif?t=1695654699\" width=616 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/3ea51c43b5bbb93391aa95cd519d787b.webm?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/3ea51c43b5bbb93391aa95cd519d787b.mp4?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>趣味十足，情节引人入胜。</strong><br>扮演星际舰队队长詹姆斯•达克，参加无数的星际作战，遨游银河系，寻找答案，为人类的生存而战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/d7d0fa34e9acb10b8ff2bfc2c567920e.poster.avif?t=1695654699\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/d7d0fa34e9acb10b8ff2bfc2c567920e.webm?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/d7d0fa34e9acb10b8ff2bfc2c567920e.mp4?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>晋级系统。</strong><br>分发经验值，完善飞船系统，安装新设备。根据你所选择的游戏风格修整飞船，或自行适应，选择最佳战术。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/8d7b8b4c9d43cadd78855a168a63046a.poster.avif?t=1695654699\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/8d7b8b4c9d43cadd78855a168a63046a.webm?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139780/extras/8d7b8b4c9d43cadd78855a168a63046a.mp4?t=1695654699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
